# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Copy this file to ".env.local" and fill in real values.
# ".env.local" is gitignored — never commit real secrets.
#
# Both values below are SAFE to expose to the browser (that's why they use the
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix). The publishable key only grants what your Supabase Row
# Level Security policies allow. Keep your SECRET key (sb_secret_...) out of
# this app entirely.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Where to get these:
#   1. Go to https://supabase.com and open (or create) your project.
#   2. In the left sidebar: Project Settings (gear icon) -> "API Keys".
#   3. Copy the "Project URL" into NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL.
#      (Also shown under Project Settings -> "Data API".)
#   4. Copy the "publishable" key (starts with sb_publishable_) into
#      NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY.
#
# Note: the publishable key is Supabase's new name for the old "anon" key. If a
# tutorial mentions an "anon" key, the publishable key is its replacement. The
# legacy anon JWT (eyJ...) still lives under the "Legacy API keys" tab, but
# prefer the publishable key.

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=sb_publishable_your-key-here

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Groq — powers food-text parsing (Phase 4). This is a SERVER-ONLY secret: it
# has NO NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix, so it never reaches the browser. Used only in
# server code (lib/food/parse.ts).
#
# Where to get it:
#   1. Go to https://console.groq.com and sign in (free).
#   2. Open "API Keys" -> "Create API Key" -> copy it (starts with gsk_...).
#   3. Paste below in .env.local, AND add it to Vercel (Project Settings ->
#      Environment Variables) so the deployed app can parse food too.
#
# Optional: override the model with GROQ_MODEL (default: llama-3.3-70b-versatile).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your-groq-key-here

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Gemini — RAG food embeddings (text-embedding-004) + coaching LLM later.
# Server-only. Get it at https://aistudio.google.com -> API keys.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-key-here

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Supabase service-role key — OFFLINE SEED SCRIPT ONLY (scripts/seed-foods.mjs).
# Full DB access, bypasses RLS. NEVER expose to the browser / never NEXT_PUBLIC_.
# Supabase -> Project Settings -> API Keys -> service_role.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-supabase-service-role-key-here
